<br />I had problems trying to run SMB with Spy vs. Spy's CHR. It never left the title screen. However, running it without a CHR chip worked fine. Running it on a CHR RAM cart also worked fine. Maybe it's just a coincidence that the values on Spy vs. Spy's CHR caused the game to lock up but the random values on the other cases didn't?

		

